Article 18: Documentation Requirements

1. Providers must keep the following documentation available for 10 years after their high-risk AI system is marketed or put into service:
   (a) Technical documentation as per Article 11;
   (b) Quality management system documentation as per Article 17;
   (c) Documentation of changes approved by notified bodies, if applicable;
   (d) Decisions and documents issued by notified bodies, if applicable;
